item.title: The Chordettes - Mr. Sandman - Ukulele Cheats
item.description: Play along video for the song Mr. Sandman by The Chordettes from the channel Ukulele Cheats. Chords used in the song: A7, A♯, A♯6, A♯7, A♯maj7, B7, C6, C7, Cm, Cm7, D7, D♯, D♯m6, D♯maj7, F, F7, Fm, F♯7, G7, Gm7, G♯m6.
